{"tid":1715360,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好辛苦 有冇手足可以教我點做？","createTime":"2019-11-13T05:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T08:02:01.000Z","uid":252022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"aae60c7ae4045e265ed288bb1035e6d71d34e62f","tid":1715360,"uid":252022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:30:14.000Z","msg":"借朋友AC post<br />\n我係25歲巴 因為當時女朋友（姐係依家老婆）有左bb 所以決定結婚，咁因為屋企都肯經濟上幫我地既關於 所以比我半工讀啦，咁我一出糧都會比萬三比老婆。但一會場運動開始 我番少左好多工 咁人工自然少左 咁變相比既家用少左。咁一開頭我都冇同佢講我出去發夢 一路都呃佢我去番工，咁依幾日我忍唔住同佢講我其實一直都有去發夢，去到今日佢已經唔比我出去 嘈到好勁 又話出去發夢全部係中學生 一去就醫生律師 反正就冇負擔既人先出去啦，但為左個仔仔 我都係選擇唔同佢嘈 番左房冷靜。<br />\n有冇人可以教我點說服到我老婆？我好想出去出分力 去幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：老婆淺黃"},{"pid":"219f8e5b2a3c71f68b634734a776ef31b8c957e3","tid":1715360,"uid":84286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:34:13.000Z","msg":"你就係為左個仔就去發夢，香港人呢鋪再輸就清袋"},{"pid":"f4b60a7025c83fd2a8651074c66453f4969062f9","tid":1715360,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:35:46.000Z","msg":"同佢講應承佢會小心d<br />\n企後排"},{"pid":"b66e19a36bdeab02ddb3abce0a2e21522fef60a5","tid":1715360,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:36:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">連登冷氣軍師 rt like reply</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">你哋已經唔使上前線搏命，係咪連呢啲都做唔到？</span><br />\n最新<br />\n<br />\n！！！！Sen. Cory Gardner (Colorado)<br />\n關注中大 支持香港<br />\n！！！！佢未cosponsor條Act 請佢幫忙！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner/status/1194341990655246346?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLadDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=cbfe541b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenCoryGardner%2Fstatus%2F1194341990655246346%3Fs%3D19&h=c0f128d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenCoryGardner